Use Case
	Fire Bullet
Actors
	User, System, Ship, Bullet
Description
	The user holds down a key representing firing a bullet. The system reads the key. The system checks the ships position and heading. 
	The system creates a bullet with the same heading as ship.
Main Course of Events
User			System								Ship					Bullet
1.Presses key
				2.Read key
 				3.Check if key represents firing
 				4.Check Ship Heading
 													5.Tell System Heading
 																			6.Create a Bullet with same 
 																				heading as ship
 																			7. Set bullet speed,ttl

Alternative Flow of Events
2.1 Wrong key. No change in system
4.1 The ship doesn't exsist